        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"387244\">Yaël Dillies</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/217875-Is-there-code-for-X.3F/topic/Equivalent.20of.20.60Or.2Eelim.60.20for.20if-then-else.2F.60Decidable.60/near/459820674\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Something like <code>simp [ite_apply, *]</code> should work, but indeed I would hope there is a specific lemma for you to use</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>It should be <code>apply_ite</code>, right? Also, my use case is covered by the <code>split</code> tactic since I'm already in tactic mode</p>",
